          "title": "ELON MUSK IS PLANNING A TEXAS UTOPIA — HIS OWN TOWN",
          "summary": "Elon Musk is planning to build a new town for his employees along the Colorado River in Texas about 35 miles from Austin. The aim of the proposed town is to create a type of Texas utopia where Musk’s employees can live and work. Musk and his top executives want their employees, particularly those at his Austin-area companies such as Tesla and SpaceX, to live in new homes with affordable rents. The site will be adjacent to Boring and SpaceX facilities which are currently being built. Pictures of the site and plans for the future city are available in the article.",
